_sText:
This was a quick creation of possible backyards that you could use in your maps. This is my first crack at it and will release other versions in the future. 

Please note that the side fence door is not operational. Also note that I placed a random door next to the stove to show there the backdoor of the house can be located. I placed it there to be used as a suggestion.

Also do not feel limited to the light I have chosen. If you want a day time environment then change the light_environment and delete the lights I have placed. 


DISCLAIMER: If you plan to add this to one of your maps then please give credit where credit is due.
